## 🔧 **CONTEXT7 CONFIGURATION**

### **MCP Client Configuration**

Add this to your MCP client configuration:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "context7": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@upstash/context7-mcp"]
    }
  }
}
```

### **Remote Configuration (Alternative)**

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "context7": {
      "url": "https://mcp.context7.com/mcp"
    }
  }
}
```

